You are building a product designer portfolio that is a faithful clone of elishajeon.com, adapted for a B2B/SaaS product designer.

## Stack
- Next.js 14 (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion
- next-themes (dark mode)
- lucide-react (icons)

## REAL values extracted from elishajeon.com

### Colors (exact)
- Background light: #F1F5FB (rgb(241, 245, 251))
- Background dark: #0F0F0F
- Text primary: rgba(0,0,0,0.75) light / rgba(255,255,255,0.85) dark
- Text muted: rgba(0,0,0,0.45) light / rgba(255,255,255,0.45) dark
- Text very muted: rgba(0,0,0,0.23)
- Accent: #E8643A
- Preview card bg: rgba(255,255,255,0.30) with backdrop-filter: blur(5px)
- Mockup card bg: rgba(0,0,0,0.03)
- Surface: #FFFFFF

### Typography (exact fonts from site)
- Display/Name: Caveat (handwritten), weight 400, letter-spacing -0.02em
  → Used for "Hiya! I'm Elisha" at 32.64px
- Heading serif: P22 Mackinac Medium (substitute: Lora or Playfair Display)
  → H1: 32px, line-height 1.2
  → H2: 22.4px, line-height 1.4, weight 500
  → H3: 18.4px, line-height 1.4
- Mono: Spline Sans Mono (substitute: JetBrains Mono)
  → Used for clock, breadcrumbs, labels: 13.28px
- UI/Body: PP Neue Montreal Medium (substitute: Inter Medium)
  → Body text: 14px, line-height 1.6

### Spacing & Layout
- Page padding: 20px sides
- Preview card (left): 308px wide, 303px tall, position absolute left 20px top 203px
- Content area (case study): 648px wide, starts at x=432px (sidebar ~220px)
- Mockup cards: border-radius 12px, bg rgba(0,0,0,0.03)
- Preview card: border-radius 8px, box-shadow rgba(79,44,9,0.06) 0px 5px 25px 3px, backdrop-filter blur(5px)

### Dock (exact)
- Position: fixed, bottom 20px, left 20px (NOT centered — left aligned!)
- Width: 230px, height: 33px
- Contains: music player info + pause indicator
- The REAL nav dock is centered bottom with icons

### Shadows
- Preview card: rgba(79, 44, 9, 0.06) 0px 5px 25px 3px (warm brown shadow)
- Mockup cards: rgba(102, 46, 0, 0) — very subtle warm shadow

## Layout — Homepage
- Top bar: name top-left in Caveat font, live clock top-right in Spline Sans Mono
- Left panel: absolute positioned, ~308px wide, preview card with project highlights
- Right canvas: floating mockup cards at different positions/z-depths, slight overlaps
  → Card 1 (Noto gradient): ~370x250px at top-right area
  → Card 2 (fitness app): ~370x250px overlapping bottom-right
  → Card 3 (OMRO product): top-right corner, smaller
  → Card 4 (dashboard): bottom-center-right
- Bottom-left: music player bar (paused state, song name)
- Bottom-center: floating dock with 5 icons
- NO top navigation
- Background: #F1F5FB

## Layout — Case Study page
- Top-left: "← Back" small link
- Top-right: theme toggle
- Left sticky sidebar: ~220px, nav items (Overview, Problem, Research, Solution, Outcome, What I Learned)
  → Active item: slightly darker, weight 500
  → Inactive: rgba(0,0,0,0.45)
  → Font: Spline Sans Mono substitute at ~13px
- Right content: 648px wide
  → Breadcrumb: "Project / Type" in mono, rgba(0,0,0,0.45)
  → H1: 32px P22 Mackinac (Lora substitute), rgba(0,0,0,0.75)
  → H2: 22.4px P22 Mackinac Medium, rgba(0,0,0,0.75)
  → Body: 14px PP Neue Montreal (Inter), line-height 1.6
  → Metadata grid: Role / Timeline / Team / Skills (pill tags)

## Layout — About page
- Left: photo card (polaroid style) + handwritten quote + signature
- Right: "About" label in mono, bio paragraphs, social links

## Layout — All Work page
- Grid of project cards, 2-3 columns
- Each card: gradient bg, project name, category tag

## Animations (Framer Motion)
- Floating mockups: y-axis loop, amplitude 10-14px, duration 4-7s, staggered delays
- Page enter: opacity 0→1 + y 16→0, 0.5s easeOut
- Card hover: scale 1.02, 0.2s
- Dock icon hover: scale 1.2, 0.15s

## Font substitutions (free/Google Fonts)
Since P22 Mackinac and PP Neue Montreal are paid fonts, use:
- Caveat → Google Fonts Caveat (exact match, free)
- P22 Mackinac → Google Fonts Lora (closest free serif)
- PP Neue Montreal → Inter (closest free sans)
- Spline Sans Mono → JetBrains Mono (closest free mono)

## Components to build
- components/Dock.tsx — bottom center floating nav
- components/Clock.tsx — live clock top right in mono
- components/TopBar.tsx — name top-left + clock top-right
- components/PreviewCard.tsx — left panel hover card
- components/MockupCanvas.tsx — right floating mockups
- components/MusicBar.tsx — bottom-left music player
- components/CaseStudySidebar.tsx — sticky left nav
- components/ProjectCard.tsx — work grid card
- lib/projects.ts — placeholder data
- app/page.tsx — homepage
- app/all-work/page.tsx — project grid
- app/work/[slug]/page.tsx — case study
- app/about/page.tsx — about

## Placeholder projects
1. "Nucleus" — SaaS analytics dashboard redesign — gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2) — tags: Redesign, B2B, Dashboard
2. "Flowdesk" — 0→1 CRM for freelancers — gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb, #f5576c) — tags: 0→1, SaaS, Mobile
3. "Arcal" — Enterprise data platform UX research — gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe, #00f2fe) — tags: Research, Enterprise, B2B
4. "Meridian" — Internal ops tool for scale-up — gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #43e97b, #38f9d7) — tags: Redesign, Ops, Desktop

## Code rules
- CSS variables in globals.css for all colors
- Dark mode via Tailwind dark: classes + next-themes
- No inline styles except dynamic values
- All animations via Framer Motion
- TypeScript strict, proper interfaces
- Import Caveat from Google Fonts in layout.tsx
